This is a '''list of restaurant terminology'''. A [[restaurant]] is a [[business]] that prepares and serves food and drink to customers in return for money, either paid before the meal, after the meal, or with a running tab. Meals are generally served and eaten on premises, but many restaurants also offer [[take-out]] and [[Delivery (commerce)|food delivery services]]. Restaurants vary greatly in appearance and offerings, including a wide variety of the main chef's [[cuisine]]s and [[Customer service|service]] models.
